      "content": "i hear what you're saying about inclusivity, but some of the other parents are really worried. they feel like these topics are too sensitive for the classroom or that it's taking away their right to teach these things to their own kids at home. why do people feel that way? it's not just about being \"unfriendly\" or whatever, there seem to be some real arguments being made there.",
